    "description": "The defining disaster of American foreign policy. 20 years, 58,220 dead, $1 trillion spent — all lost when Saigon fell in 1975.",
    "costNominal": 168000000000,
    "costInflationAdjusted": 1000000000000,
    "costYear": 2023,
    "usCasualties": {
      "deaths": 58220,
      "wounded": 153303,
      "battleDeaths": 47434,
      "missing": 1584
