    "congressionalAuth": false,
    "authDetail": "Gulf of Tonkin Resolution (1964) — later revealed to be based on fabricated intelligence. Never a formal declaration of war.",
    "keyEvents": [
      "Geneva Accords signed (July 21, 1954) - Temporarily divide Vietnam at 17th parallel, elections scheduled for 1956",
