        "role": "President of the United States",
        "note": "Delayed intervention for three years, then committed U.S. forces without congressional authorization after Srebrenica made inaction politically untenable."
      },
      {
        "name": "Ratko Mladić",
        "role": "Bosnian Serb Military Commander",
        "note": "Directed the Srebrenica massacre and the siege of Sarajevo. Convicted of genocide by the International Criminal Tribunal."
      },
      {
        "name": "Radovan Karadžić",
