    "outcomeDetail": "The \"war on terror\" has no defined enemy, no defined battlefield, and no defined end. After 25 years and trillions of dollars, terrorism still exists.",
    "congressionalAuth": false,
    "authDetail": "All conducted under the 2001 AUMF — a 60-word authorization written in 3 days that has been used to justify military operations in at least 22 countries.",
