    "description": "US built a $110M drone base in Agadez, Niger and deployed ~1,100 troops to fight ISIS and al-Qaeda affiliates in the Sahel. After the 2023 Niger coup, the junta expelled US forces. Full withdrawal completed 2024. Four US soldiers killed in 2017 Tongo Tongo ambush.",
    "costNominal": 500000000,
    "costInflationAdjusted": 600000000,
    "costYear": 2024,
    "usCasualties": {
