    "civilianDeaths": 0,
    "troopsDeployed": 1100,
    "outcome": "Withdrawal",
    "outcomeDetail": "US expelled after Niger coup. $110M drone base abandoned. ISIS and al-Qaeda affiliates remain active in the Sahel. Wagner/Russia replaced US influence.",
    "congressionalAuth": false,
    "authDetail": "Conducted under 2001 AUMF. Most Americans unaware US troops were in Niger until the 2017 ambush.",
