      "Iraq",
      "Syria"
    ],
    "description": "Operation Inherent Resolve — US-led coalition against ISIS/ISIL after they captured Mosul and declared a \"caliphate.\" Over 34,000 airstrikes. ISIS territorial caliphate defeated by 2019 but insurgency continues. 2,500 US troops remain in Iraq and 900 in Syria as of 2026.",
    "costNominal": 108000000000,
    "costInflationAdjusted": 115000000000,
    "costYear": 2024,
    "usCasualties": {
      "deaths": 93,
      "wounded": 300,
      "battleDeaths": 93,
      "missing": 0
    },
    "civilianDeaths": 13000,
    "troopsDeployed": 5000,
    "outcome": "Partial Victory",
    "outcomeDetail": "ISIS territorial caliphate destroyed by 2019. But ISIS insurgency continues. 3,400 US troops still deployed in Iraq and Syria. No exit plan.",
    "congressionalAuth": false,
    "authDetail": "Obama used 2001 AUMF (designed for 9/11 attackers) to justify war against ISIS — a group that didn't exist in 2001 and was actually fighting al-Qaeda.",
    "keyEvents": [
      {
        "year": 2014,
        "event": "ISIS captures Mosul; declares caliphate. US airstrikes begin August"
      },
      {
        "year": 2015,
        "event": "US deploys Special Forces to Syria"
      },
      {
