    "description": "Following Russia's full-scale invasion of Ukraine in February 2022, the US provided $66.9 billion in military aid including HIMARS, Patriot missiles, Abrams tanks, and F-16 training. The largest US military aid package since WWII Lend-Lease. No US troops deployed in combat.",
    "costNominal": 66900000000,
    "costInflationAdjusted": 66900000000,
    "costYear": 2025,
    "usCasualties": {
