    "libertarianNote": "The US spent billions bombing one of the poorest countries on earth to protect shipping lanes for multinational corporations. The Houthis, armed with cheap drones and missiles, cost the US hundreds of millions to counter — a perfect example of asymmetric warfare draining the empire.",
